                        <li><strong>Outcome:</strong> Faster convergence to correct answers, compounding skill development, and a sustainable edge over one-shot prompters.</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
                <p>I've spent the last six months building websites, writing content, and automating workflows with AI. The single biggest unlock wasn't a better prompt. It was accepting that <strong>AI will never one-shot my problems</strong>.</p>
                <p>And that's not a bug. It's a feature.</p>
